{"tid":1549772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］聽日去美領好大鑊！","createTime":"2019-09-07T12:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T12:45:02.000Z","uid":316802,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ea96e354d5737173d03bb26a07f932d716b5b2dd","tid":1549772,"uid":316802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:32:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家聽日美領見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UQFQiqm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUQFQiqm.jpg&h=c5a0a26e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家順便入埋下面個po温下人權法案係乜，訪問都唔洗比人問到口啞啞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我屌哂你班對「香港人權與民主法案」一知半解既人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549246\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549246</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"},{"pid":"669274bf7f704503726ade6f177fd4456ee6a9b1","tid":1549772,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:33:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b9990d01d986f8369abd6436cc0732f3adece9c","tid":1549772,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:33:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9558b4dff3732a946f595e7fda737a48042295e","tid":1549772,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>九月八，遮打見！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ZUq8PfJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUq8PfJ.png&h=6ed8457a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><ins><span style=\"color: purple;\">最好2點半前到達簽署！</span></ins></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k5RDr3G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk5RDr3G.jpg&h=fc849298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">記定英文口號</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mq23Dbz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMq23Dbz.png&h=28cc984b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8azEVYe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8azEVYe.png&h=f85b965a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W8g0FpV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW8g0FpV.png&h=b3716331&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">最後唔好意思阻多你十分鐘睇睇人權法其實係咩黎</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/十分鐘-了解-香港人權與民主法案\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%8D%81%E5%88%86%E9%90%98-%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E8%88%87%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uCHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=e9452738\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%8D%81%E5%88%86%E9%90%98-%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E8%88%87%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88&h=cd5a124f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/十分鐘-了解-香港人權與民主法案</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不衝擊，不破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>九月八，美領見！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a9853d9e20d0f47d9fa6e684f01a09ac031527","tid":1549772,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:34:36.000Z","msg":"借之前一個巴打寫嘅文一用<br />\n<br />\n佢哋大搖大擺行出警察宿舍，<br />\n每一個警察行過，都陰陰嘴笑鳩你班香港人：<br />\n「光復香港喎，時代革命喎。」<br />\n「曱甴。」<br />\n<br />\n每一個圍過警署嘅街坊，<br />\n都要接受依一班警察，<br />\n仲有佢哋家屬嘅冷眼。<br />\n「嗰隻甴曱啊，」佢指住你，<br />\n「嗰日佢咪圍鳩咗喺到囉，<br />\n依家咪死狗咁。」<br />\n<br />\n你忍唔住，你屌鳩佢老母。<br />\n不過佢一啲都無怕過你，<br />\n「甴曱！收皮啦！你打鳩我啊？！」<br />\n佢行埋嚟，再摸下你個頭，<br />\n「戇鳩仔。」<br />\n你忍住，你知道你唔可能打返佢。<br />\n佢拍拍你塊臉，<br />\n「點啊？你唔打鳩我喇？」<br />\n佢一啲收手嘅意欲都無，<br />\n因為警察已經為所欲為：<br />\n「又話黑警死全家？我全家仲喺到喎。」<br />\n<br />\n宿舍隔離就係警署，<br />\n警察一嚟到就會將你搭入去。<br />\n無人知道裏面會發生咩事。<br />\n你可能會畀人打一身、<br />\n畀人彈春袋、玩屎忽。<br />\n你女朋友喺你隔離，<br />\n你唔知道佢畀人拉埋入去之後會發生咩事，<br />\n你保護唔到你女朋友。<br />\n<br />\n「我要你同我道歉。」<br />\n警察一家望實你，同你講。<br />\n你唔敢再生事端。<br />\n「對唔住，好對唔住。」<br />\n最後你向警察道歉。<br />\n佢一邊拍你塊臉，一邊同你講，<br />\n「下次唔好喇。」<br />\n你覺得好興幸，<br />\n警察肯原諒你。<br />\n<br />\n依一個就係香港人放棄嘅結局，<br />\n你班「曱甴」依家想放棄未？"},{"pid":"fe639c7cac1bbed064392223f67b3086d5a59396","tid":1549772,"uid":273265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:35:07.000Z","msg":"[外國文宣] 眾籌網上賣廣告有人會課金嗎?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547011</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1d4d13af09d3df711398ffe25f5cc25e2faaf2c0","tid":1549772,"uid":316802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:35:16.000Z","msg":"P牌仔求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969d29fa3da047817bcc222018e6ceef9e80f8ad","tid":1549772,"uid":8532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1acd736281c63c099efcc6eec32cdae5d6912